    <title>Deleting entities from the editor</title>
    <shortdesc>The CWRC-Writer templates come with pre existing <?oxy_insert_start author="ilovan" timestamp="20140928T232620-0600"?>entity annotations<?oxy_insert_end?> as examples to new users. You can easily delete these <?oxy_delete author="ilovan" timestamp="20140928T232636-0600" content="entities or any entities"?><?oxy_insert_start author="ilovan" timestamp="20140928T232636-0600"?>annotations or any annotations<?oxy_insert_end?> that you don't want in your document from within the editor (using right-click). </shortdesc>
